 <div class="leftblock">
    <h2>We are independently audited by the <a href="http://www.ukas.com/technical-information/technical-committee/absestos-tac/Asbestos-TAC.asp" target="_blank">United Kingdom Accreditation Service</a> (UKAS) to ensure the accuracy and accountability of all tests and inspection reports produced for our customers</h2>
    <ul class="ukas">
        <li><a href="http://www.ukas.org/testing/lab_detail.asp?lab_id=530" target="_blank"><img src="/images/ukastesting.gif" alt="United Kingdom Accreditation Service (UKAS), Testing (1227)" width="80" /></a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.ukas.com/InspectionBodySearch.asp?qt=Envirochem" target="_blank" ><img src="/images/ukasinspection.gif" alt="United Kingdom Accreditation Service (UKAS), Inspection (0260) "width="80" /></a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/business/regulation/31835.aspx" target="_blank"><img src="/images/mcerts.png" alt="Environment Agency, MCERTS" width="80" /></a></li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="list">
        <li>Envirochem participates in the <a href="http://www.hsl.gov.uk/centres-of-excellence/proficiency-testing-schemes/rice.aspx" target="_blank">RICE</a> and <a href="http://www.hsl.gov.uk/centres-of-excellence/proficiency-testing-schemes/aims.aspx" target="_blank">AIMS</a> proficiency test schemes</li>
        <li>We are UKAS accredited for asbestos sampling, <a href="?p=asbestos&amp;t=fibre-identification">fibre identification</a>, <a href="?p=asbestos&amp;t=surveys">surveying</a>, <a href="?p=asbestos&amp;t=air-monitoring">air monitoring and fibre counting</a>.</li>
        <li>We are members of <a href="http://www.tica-acad.co.uk/" target="_blank">ACAD</a> and <a href="http://www.arca.org.uk/" target="_blank">ARCA</a>, <a href="http://www.chas.gov.uk/" target="_blank">CHAS</a> and <a href="http://www.constructionline.co.uk/static/about-us.html" target="_blank">Construction Line</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="http://www.bohs.org/" target="_blank"><img class="floatright" src="/images/bohslogo.gif" alt="British Occupational Hygiene Society (MCERTS)" width="200" /></a>
    <p>All of our consultants, project managers, chemists, analysts, surveyors and laboratory technicians hold nationally recognised qualifications relevant to their roles (including P401, P402, P403, P404, P405, etc.) through the <a href="http://www.bohs.org/" target="_blank">British Occupational Hygiene Society</a> (BOHS).</p>
    <p>They all have years of experience in the industry, are trained to <a href="http://www.ukas.com/technical-information/technical-committee/absestos-tac/Asbestos-TAC.asp" target="_blank">UKAS specifications</a> and carry out all work within accordance to <a href="http://www.hse.gov.uk/asbestos/" target="_blank">HSE Guidance Notes</a>.</p>
    <p>Many of our surveyors have additional qualifications, specific training and safety equipment such as to work in confined spaces, high level and other potentially hazardous areas.</p>
</div>
